1292
01:25:28,619 --> 01:25:29,920
[SPEAKER_01] Kako gledate na to?

1293
01:25:29,920 --> 01:25:31,899
[SPEAKER_00] Jako negativno.

1294
01:25:31,899 --> 01:25:34,619
[SPEAKER_01] Sad je malo bezobrazno

1295
01:25:34,619 --> 01:25:36,699
[SPEAKER_01] da ja pitam u Monaku, toga sigurno nema.

1296
01:25:36,699 --> 01:25:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ima.

1297
01:25:37,539 --> 01:25:38,640
[SPEAKER_00] U Monaku toga nema.

1298
01:25:38,640 --> 01:25:41,060
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, ima svugdje drugdje.

1299
01:25:41,060 --> 01:25:43,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ima u Italiju, u Francuskoj, u Engleskoj,

1300
01:25:43,619 --> 01:25:44,859
[SPEAKER_00] u Belgiji, u Švedskoj,

1301
01:25:44,859 --> 01:25:45,800
[SPEAKER_00] u Norveškoj, svugdje.

1302
01:25:45,800 --> 01:25:50,479
[SPEAKER_00] I to se nema ni u Mađarskoj.

1303
01:25:50,479 --> 01:25:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako padne Orban,

1304
01:25:52,539 --> 01:25:53,520
[SPEAKER_00] bit će i u Mađarskoj.

1305
01:25:53,520 --> 01:25:54,300
[SPEAKER_01] A hoće li pasti?

1306
01:25:54,300 --> 01:25:55,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam.

1307
01:25:56,319 --> 01:25:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] Šta vam nos vaš kaže?

1308
01:25:58,539 --> 01:26:01,899
[SPEAKER_00] 50% ili hoće ili neće.

1309
01:26:01,899 --> 01:26:05,760
[SPEAKER_01] Sad nećete bubnuti župa.

1310
01:26:05,760 --> 01:26:08,779
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajte, imamo ove tu

1311
01:26:08,779 --> 01:26:10,880
[SPEAKER_00] ispitivanja javnog mijenja,

1312
01:26:10,880 --> 01:26:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali ispitivanja javnog mijenja

1313
01:26:13,119 --> 01:26:15,420
[SPEAKER_00] će dati šta naručitelj želi da da.

1314
01:26:15,420 --> 01:26:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ne možemo vjerovat šta se tamo.

1315
01:26:17,960 --> 01:26:19,600
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je sad teško uopće

1316
01:26:19,600 --> 01:26:21,520
[SPEAKER_00] pojmiti da bi Mađari

1317
01:26:21,520 --> 01:26:23,460
[SPEAKER_00] mogli izazvati ovoga

1318
01:26:23,460 --> 01:26:24,560
[SPEAKER_00] Mađara.

1319
01:26:25,159 --> 01:26:28,079
[SPEAKER_00] jer šta bi onda...

1320
01:26:28,079 --> 01:26:29,539
[SPEAKER_01] Koji vodi u svim anketama.

1321
01:26:29,539 --> 01:26:32,060
[SPEAKER_00] Koji navodno vodi u svim anketama.

1322
01:26:32,060 --> 01:26:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ano je ključna riječ navodno.

1323
01:26:33,800 --> 01:26:36,779
[SPEAKER_00] Dajte, znači, šta su se sad Mađari

1324
01:26:36,779 --> 01:26:39,020
[SPEAKER_00] na jedan put domisluje da bi oni ipak želili

1325
01:26:39,020 --> 01:26:40,500
[SPEAKER_00] da im je zemlja preplavljena

1326
01:26:40,500 --> 01:26:43,520
[SPEAKER_00] migrantima, da imaju LGBT parade.

1327
01:26:46,220 --> 01:26:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali možda im je dosta već orbana.

1328
01:26:48,000 --> 01:26:50,600
[SPEAKER_01] Možda im je dosta, ne znam kako kažu, korupcije.

1329
01:26:50,600 --> 01:26:52,619
[SPEAKER_01] Nemam pojma.

1330
01:26:52,619 --> 01:26:53,479
[SPEAKER_01] Evo pa sad imate

1331
01:26:53,479 --> 01:26:55,319
[SPEAKER_01] Mađarska i Slovačka

1332
01:26:55,319 --> 01:26:56,819
[SPEAKER_01] vode energetski rat.

1333
01:26:56,819 --> 01:26:58,220
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da sam to rekla na početku.

1334
01:26:58,220 --> 01:27:01,140
[SPEAKER_01] Odnosno naftni rat, sukob sa Ukrajinom.

1335
01:27:01,140 --> 01:27:05,899
[SPEAKER_01] Tu je nekako i Hrvatska upletena

1336
01:27:05,899 --> 01:27:07,020
[SPEAKER_01] zbog našeg Janafa.

1337
01:27:07,020 --> 01:27:09,180
[SPEAKER_01] Rekla je danas Evropska komisija

1338
01:27:09,180 --> 01:27:11,199
[SPEAKER_01] da neka Hrvatska sama odluči

1339
01:27:11,199 --> 01:27:16,100
[SPEAKER_01] hoće li sirovu rusku naftu

1340
01:27:16,100 --> 01:27:18,699
[SPEAKER_01] kroz naš Janaf distribuirati.

1341
01:27:18,699 --> 01:27:21,520
[SPEAKER_00] Da si sprljamo naš naftovod

1342
01:27:21,520 --> 01:27:22,939
[SPEAKER_00] sa ruskom naftom, a nikad.

1343
01:27:22,939 --> 01:27:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] Najšalni se, naravno.

1344
01:27:25,659 --> 01:27:27,159
[SPEAKER_00] Gledajte, ja ne znam,

1345
01:27:27,159 --> 01:27:29,420
[SPEAKER_00] jer šta bi to značilo

1346
01:27:29,420 --> 01:27:31,100
[SPEAKER_00] da onda Mađari žele odustati

1347
01:27:31,100 --> 01:27:32,100
[SPEAKER_00] od svoje pozicije,

1348
01:27:32,100 --> 01:27:33,319
[SPEAKER_00] od svog suvereniteta

1349
01:27:33,319 --> 01:27:34,659
[SPEAKER_00] zato što ih ovi ucijenjuju.

1350
01:27:34,659 --> 01:27:38,699
[SPEAKER_00] A oni su susjedi sa Ukrajinom.

1351
01:27:38,699 --> 01:27:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ako se rat proširi,

1352
01:27:40,739 --> 01:27:43,819
[SPEAKER_00] prvo će zahvatiti

1353
01:27:43,819 --> 01:27:45,800
[SPEAKER_00] susjedne zemlje Ukrajine,

1354
01:27:45,800 --> 01:27:48,579
[SPEAKER_00] među njima i Mađarsku,

1355
01:27:48,579 --> 01:27:52,640
[SPEAKER_00] a u Mađarskoj se već Ukrajina

1356
01:27:52,640 --> 01:27:55,279
[SPEAKER_00] zlostavlja mađarsku manjinu.

1357
01:27:55,279 --> 01:27:58,199
[SPEAKER_00] I već su tu

1358
01:27:58,199 --> 01:28:02,279
[SPEAKER_00] po malo kipi

1359
01:28:02,279 --> 01:28:06,340
[SPEAKER_00] sukob između te dvije strane.

1360
01:28:06,340 --> 01:28:09,239
[SPEAKER_00] I sad, koja je reakcija

1361
01:28:09,239 --> 01:28:11,100
[SPEAKER_00] običnog naroda na to da kaže

1362
01:28:11,100 --> 01:28:13,539
[SPEAKER_00] pa dobro, pritišću nas,

1363
01:28:13,539 --> 01:28:15,899
[SPEAKER_00] ajde, ajde, ajde, ajmo se pustiti.

1364
01:28:15,899 --> 01:28:17,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo odustati.

1365
01:28:17,359 --> 01:28:21,960
[SPEAKER_00] Prekinuli su nam dovod nafte

1366
01:28:21,960 --> 01:28:23,520
[SPEAKER_00] zato što im nećemo da,

1367
01:28:23,520 --> 01:28:26,039
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam koliko milijardi...

1368
01:28:26,039 --> 01:28:29,859
[SPEAKER_01] 90 milijardi eura je blokirala

1369
01:28:29,859 --> 01:28:30,600
[SPEAKER_01] zbog toga, Mađarska.

1370
01:28:30,600 --> 01:28:32,880
[SPEAKER_00] 90 milijardi nije to sve od Mađara,

1371
01:28:32,880 --> 01:28:34,180
[SPEAKER_00] jedan dio od Mađara, ali...

1372
01:28:34,180 --> 01:28:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, sve te zavrzlame

1373
01:28:37,079 --> 01:28:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] raste pritisak na Mađarsku

1374
01:28:40,000 --> 01:28:42,960
[SPEAKER_00] i sad, ajmo odustati od sebe

1375
01:28:42,960 --> 01:28:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] da bi mogli imati

1376
01:28:45,000 --> 01:28:48,100
[SPEAKER_00] LGBT parade i imigrante

1377
01:28:48,100 --> 01:28:50,439
[SPEAKER_00] i da nam dolazi nafta.

1378
01:28:50,439 --> 01:28:52,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne znam, ovaj...

1379
01:28:52,920 --> 01:28:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, meni je...

1380
01:28:54,960 --> 01:28:57,060
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam čitati Mađarsku,

1381
01:28:57,060 --> 01:29:00,079
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam kako bi javno raspoloženje

1382
01:29:00,079 --> 01:29:01,220
[SPEAKER_00] unutar Mađarske

1383
01:29:01,220 --> 01:29:04,840
[SPEAKER_00] interpretirao,

1384
01:29:04,840 --> 01:29:07,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali šta dolazi kroz...

1385
01:29:07,460 --> 01:29:11,300
[SPEAKER_00] Šta dolazi kroz ove javne medije,

1386
01:29:11,300 --> 01:29:12,640
[SPEAKER_00] to ne vjerujem ništa.

1387
01:29:12,739 --> 01:29:15,340
[SPEAKER_00] Više sam sklon da suprotno mislim

1388
01:29:15,340 --> 01:29:16,739
[SPEAKER_00] od onoga što nam serviraju.

1389
01:29:16,739 --> 01:29:18,380
[SPEAKER_01] Neka Mađari sami odluče

1390
01:29:18,380 --> 01:29:19,340
[SPEAKER_01] o svojoj sudbini.

1391
01:29:19,340 --> 01:29:21,680
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, naravno, zato što smo

1392
01:29:21,680 --> 01:29:22,760
[SPEAKER_00] nije demokracija

1393
01:29:22,760 --> 01:29:24,500
[SPEAKER_00] i mi držimo do ljudskih prava

1394
01:29:24,500 --> 01:29:27,500
[SPEAKER_00] i parlamentarnog...

1395
01:29:27,500 --> 01:29:29,140
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se to već zove.

1396
01:29:29,140 --> 01:29:30,140
[SPEAKER_00] Sve te ljepe stvari.

1397
01:29:30,140 --> 01:29:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko pratite, gospodine Krajner,

1398
01:29:32,000 --> 01:29:33,159
[SPEAKER_01] događanja u Hrvatskoj?

1399
01:29:33,159 --> 01:29:38,319
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, uglavnom, površno i malo

1400
01:29:38,319 --> 01:29:41,199
[SPEAKER_00] i uglavnom kada sam u Hrvatskoj.

1401
01:29:41,279 --> 01:29:42,680
[SPEAKER_00] jer onda neizbježno

1402
01:29:42,680 --> 01:29:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] to vidimo u novinama

1403
01:29:44,920 --> 01:29:48,260
[SPEAKER_00] i na televiziji i tako dalje.

1404
01:29:48,260 --> 01:29:51,880
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što me svaki put malo iznenadi

1405
01:29:51,880 --> 01:29:53,960
[SPEAKER_00] je da mi joj živimo u 40-im godinama.

1406
01:29:53,960 --> 01:29:56,220
[SPEAKER_00] Jer se neprestano govori

1407
01:29:56,220 --> 01:29:57,880
[SPEAKER_00] o Ustašama i Četmicima.

1408
01:29:57,880 --> 01:30:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je baš malo mutno.

1409
01:30:01,720 --> 01:30:06,060
[SPEAKER_00] zašto smo toliko obsjednuti

1410
01:30:06,060 --> 01:30:09,300
[SPEAKER_00] pitanjima koje više ne možemo riješiti.

1411
01:30:09,300 --> 01:30:11,800
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, ušao sam u polemiku

1412
01:30:11,800 --> 01:30:15,439
[SPEAKER_00] s jednim čovjekom na internetu

1413
01:30:15,439 --> 01:30:17,119
[SPEAKER_00] preko e-maila.

1414
01:30:19,119 --> 01:30:22,560
[SPEAKER_00] ovako malo, rekuo bi da malo mi je desničario

1415
01:30:22,560 --> 01:30:24,840
[SPEAKER_00] po uporukama.

1416
01:30:24,840 --> 01:30:27,800
[SPEAKER_00] I sad,

1417
01:30:27,800 --> 01:30:32,380
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam spomenuo, pa nismo baš u jako dobroj situaciji.

1418
01:30:32,380 --> 01:30:33,640
[SPEAKER_00] Sad nam je prva,

1419
01:30:33,640 --> 01:30:36,720
[SPEAKER_00] najveća manjina u Hrvatskoj su nam

1420
01:30:36,720 --> 01:30:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] Hindusi, Indici i Nepalci.

1421
01:30:39,380 --> 01:30:41,380
[SPEAKER_00] To nije,

1422
01:30:41,380 --> 01:30:43,260
[SPEAKER_00] mislim,

1423
01:30:43,260 --> 01:30:44,300
[SPEAKER_00] šta god,

1424
01:30:44,300 --> 01:30:47,140
[SPEAKER_00] kakav god čovjek imao stav prema Srbima,

1425
01:30:47,140 --> 01:30:48,180
[SPEAKER_00] Srbi su ipak

1426
01:30:48,180 --> 01:30:51,560
[SPEAKER_00] isti jezik govorimo,

1427
01:30:51,560 --> 01:30:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] isto izgledamo.

1428
01:30:53,119 --> 01:30:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] Kršćani su.

1429
01:30:55,619 --> 01:30:59,899
[SPEAKER_00] Ako nam nije kultura ista,

1430
01:30:59,899 --> 01:31:00,760
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo je slična.

1431
01:31:00,760 --> 01:31:01,680
[SPEAKER_00] Razumijemo se.

1432
01:31:01,680 --> 01:31:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] I ovdje su stoljećima.

1433
01:31:04,199 --> 01:31:05,880
[SPEAKER_01] I napali su nas.

1434
01:31:06,720 --> 01:31:08,060
[SPEAKER_01] gamovinski rat.

1435
01:31:08,060 --> 01:31:11,180
[SPEAKER_00] Da, napali su nas.

1436
01:31:11,180 --> 01:31:12,340
[SPEAKER_01] Znate, to je,

1437
01:31:12,340 --> 01:31:15,140
[SPEAKER_01] u Hrvatskoj kolektivnoj svijesti

1438
01:31:15,140 --> 01:31:17,720
[SPEAKER_01] je to pečat koji...

1439
01:31:17,720 --> 01:31:18,920
[SPEAKER_00] To se kad desilo?

1440
01:31:18,920 --> 01:31:20,180
[SPEAKER_00] Prije 30 godina.

1441
01:31:20,180 --> 01:31:22,739
[SPEAKER_00] A oni su tu stoljećima.

1442
01:31:22,739 --> 01:31:25,159
[SPEAKER_00] I zašto su nas napali?

1443
01:31:25,159 --> 01:31:27,060
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ih je neko

1444
01:31:27,060 --> 01:31:28,899
[SPEAKER_00] na to nahuškao.

1445
01:31:28,899 --> 01:31:30,520
[SPEAKER_00] A to,

1446
01:31:30,520 --> 01:31:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] trebamo biti svjesni

1447
01:31:32,960 --> 01:31:34,779
[SPEAKER_00] da to se

1448
01:31:34,779 --> 01:31:36,699
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek i stalno dešava

1449
01:31:36,699 --> 01:31:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] u svijetu.

1450
01:31:37,380 --> 01:31:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ako neko želi

1451
01:31:38,659 --> 01:31:40,659
[SPEAKER_00] destabilizirati neki prostor,

1452
01:31:40,659 --> 01:31:42,159
[SPEAKER_00] uzeti će neku manjinu,

1453
01:31:42,159 --> 01:31:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] napunit će ih strahom

1454
01:31:48,840 --> 01:31:50,859
[SPEAKER_00] i nahuškat će ih

1455
01:31:50,859 --> 01:31:53,159
[SPEAKER_00] da krenu

1456
01:31:53,159 --> 01:31:54,159
[SPEAKER_00] u sukobe.

1457
01:31:54,159 --> 01:31:56,159
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

1458
01:31:56,159 --> 01:31:57,579
[SPEAKER_00] tako je počeo,

1459
01:31:57,579 --> 01:31:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] tako je recimo

1460
01:31:58,500 --> 01:31:59,460
[SPEAKER_00] drugi svjetski rat

1461
01:31:59,460 --> 01:32:00,520
[SPEAKER_00] u Češkoj počeo.

1462
01:32:00,619 --> 01:32:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] Hitler je krenuo

1463
01:32:04,960 --> 01:32:06,159
[SPEAKER_00] nahuškavati

1464
01:32:06,159 --> 01:32:07,880
[SPEAKER_00] ove njemce,

1465
01:32:07,880 --> 01:32:08,640
[SPEAKER_00] sudete,

1466
01:32:08,640 --> 01:32:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] protiv Češke.

1467
01:32:10,039 --> 01:32:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] I onda,

1468
01:32:12,119 --> 01:32:13,319
[SPEAKER_00] takve iste stvari

1469
01:32:13,319 --> 01:32:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] vam se dešavaju

1470
01:32:14,159 --> 01:32:15,840
[SPEAKER_00] između Grka i Turaka,

1471
01:32:15,840 --> 01:32:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] između Armenaca

1472
01:32:17,539 --> 01:32:18,899
[SPEAKER_00] i Azerbejdžanaca,

1473
01:32:18,899 --> 01:32:21,640
[SPEAKER_00] između Kineza i Japanaca.

1474
01:32:22,640 --> 01:32:25,979
[SPEAKER_00] To nije neko neprijateljstvo

1475
01:32:25,979 --> 01:32:27,260
[SPEAKER_00] koje postoji tamo

1476
01:32:27,260 --> 01:32:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] zato što je to neizbježno tako,

1477
01:32:29,699 --> 01:32:31,659
[SPEAKER_00] zato što se ti ljudi

1478
01:32:31,659 --> 01:32:34,520
[SPEAKER_00] onako neiskorjenjivo mrze,

1479
01:32:34,520 --> 01:32:36,220
[SPEAKER_00] nego je to

1480
01:32:36,220 --> 01:32:39,659
[SPEAKER_00] hotimično iscenirano

1481
01:32:39,659 --> 01:32:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] izvana.

1482
01:32:40,159 --> 01:32:42,159
[SPEAKER_00] Znate, govorili smo ono i...

1483
01:32:42,159 --> 01:32:43,239
[SPEAKER_01] Prvi put ste to kod mene

1484
01:32:43,239 --> 01:32:44,859
[SPEAKER_01] rekli, staklenke i mrave.

1485
01:32:44,859 --> 01:32:47,220
[SPEAKER_00] Staklenke sa crvenim i crvim mravima.

1486
01:32:47,220 --> 01:32:49,340
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mravi se ne napadaju

1487
01:32:49,340 --> 01:32:50,640
[SPEAKER_00] dok neko tu staklenku

1488
01:32:50,640 --> 01:32:52,920
[SPEAKER_00] dobro ne potrese.

1489
01:32:52,920 --> 01:32:54,640
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, znači mi,

1490
01:32:54,640 --> 01:32:57,760
[SPEAKER_00] umjesto da smo psjednuti Srbima,

1491
01:32:57,760 --> 01:32:59,819
[SPEAKER_00] mi bi trebali biti psjednuti

1492
01:32:59,819 --> 01:33:01,359
[SPEAKER_00] ko nam trese staklenku.

1493
01:33:01,359 --> 01:33:03,520
[SPEAKER_00] Jer kako su nam je potresli

1494
01:33:03,520 --> 01:33:04,560
[SPEAKER_00] između nas i Srba,

1495
01:33:04,560 --> 01:33:06,119
[SPEAKER_00] mogu sutra je potresti

1496
01:33:06,119 --> 01:33:07,819
[SPEAKER_00] između Hrvata i tih Indijaca

1497
01:33:07,819 --> 01:33:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] i Nepalaca.

1498
01:33:08,539 --> 01:33:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] I tako da

1499
01:33:14,260 --> 01:33:17,039
[SPEAKER_00] mi radi svoje budućnosti

1500
01:33:17,039 --> 01:33:18,020
[SPEAKER_00] i svoje sigurnosti

1501
01:33:18,020 --> 01:33:19,020
[SPEAKER_00] moramo tim stvarima

1502
01:33:19,020 --> 01:33:20,199
[SPEAKER_00] voditi računa,

1503
01:33:20,399 --> 01:33:21,819
[SPEAKER_00] a ne se povoditi

1504
01:33:21,819 --> 01:33:23,520
[SPEAKER_00] za...

1505
01:33:23,520 --> 01:33:29,520
[SPEAKER_00] znači, povoditi se ljenim razmišljanjem,

1506
01:33:29,520 --> 01:33:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] emocionalnim nekakvim obsesijama

1507
01:33:35,460 --> 01:33:39,659
[SPEAKER_00] i impulzivnim reakcijama.

1508
01:33:40,520 --> 01:33:42,479
[SPEAKER_00] znači, ako vam je neko tu

1509
01:33:42,479 --> 01:33:44,420
[SPEAKER_00] koji dijeli vašu kulturu,

1510
01:33:44,420 --> 01:33:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] koji govori vaš jezik,

1511
01:33:45,619 --> 01:33:46,859
[SPEAKER_00] koji izgleda isto kao vi

1512
01:33:46,859 --> 01:33:48,140
[SPEAKER_00] i sa kojima ste

1513
01:33:48,140 --> 01:33:50,640
[SPEAKER_00] ono isprepleteni stoljećima

1514
01:33:50,640 --> 01:33:52,140
[SPEAKER_00] mješanih brakova i svega,

1515
01:33:52,140 --> 01:33:53,359
[SPEAKER_00] mislim, šta zna, ja sam Hrvat,

1516
01:33:53,939 --> 01:33:57,560
[SPEAKER_00] moja obitelj je dolazi od svuda pomalo,

1517
01:33:57,560 --> 01:34:00,159
[SPEAKER_00] iz Slovenije i iz Češke,

1518
01:34:00,159 --> 01:34:04,319
[SPEAKER_00] i iz Italije i iz Srbije i iz Dalmacije.

1519
01:34:04,859 --> 01:34:05,939
[SPEAKER_00] i znači, ja ako idem

1520
01:34:05,939 --> 01:34:07,479
[SPEAKER_00] tri, četiri generacije,

1521
01:34:07,479 --> 01:34:09,300
[SPEAKER_00] moje Hrvatstvo je biti

1522
01:34:09,300 --> 01:34:12,640
[SPEAKER_00] moj nekakav kulturni identitet.

1523
01:34:13,340 --> 01:34:15,720
[SPEAKER_00] meni da neko ide brojat krvna zrca,

1524
01:34:15,720 --> 01:34:17,520
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam šta bi izašlo van.

1525
01:34:17,520 --> 01:34:18,399
[SPEAKER_01] Šta bi našao, jel da?

1526
01:34:18,399 --> 01:34:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ali pretpostavljam da je tako

1527
01:34:19,699 --> 01:34:21,340
[SPEAKER_00] za velik dio Hrvatstva,

1528
01:34:21,340 --> 01:34:23,239
[SPEAKER_00] jer ovdje je prolazilo,

1529
01:34:23,239 --> 01:34:24,739
[SPEAKER_00] prolazio je Napoleon

1530
01:34:24,739 --> 01:34:25,880
[SPEAKER_00] sa svojim vojskama,

1531
01:34:25,880 --> 01:34:27,760
[SPEAKER_00] Austro-Ugari, Italijani,

1532
01:34:27,760 --> 01:34:28,979
[SPEAKER_00] Mlećani, Turci,

1533
01:34:28,979 --> 01:34:31,039
[SPEAKER_00] svašto je tu bilo.

1534
01:34:31,039 --> 01:34:32,680
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ne možemo išći

1535
01:34:32,680 --> 01:34:33,720
[SPEAKER_00] za krvnim zrcima,

1536
01:34:33,720 --> 01:34:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] ali moramo uzimati kulturu

1537
01:34:35,960 --> 01:34:39,880
[SPEAKER_00] kao nešto što stvara,

1538
01:34:39,880 --> 01:34:42,180
[SPEAKER_00] što daje društvu

1539
01:34:42,180 --> 01:34:44,140
[SPEAKER_00] kohezivnost je tako.

1540
01:34:44,140 --> 01:34:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] I sad, ako ste jednu manjinu

1541
01:34:47,960 --> 01:34:48,899
[SPEAKER_00] zamijenili nekom

1542
01:34:48,899 --> 01:34:51,439
[SPEAKER_00] koja vam je to potpuno strano tijelo,

1543
01:34:51,439 --> 01:34:54,300
[SPEAKER_00] čemu se možemo nadati s toga?

1544
01:34:54,300 --> 01:34:56,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam, ali možemo pogledati

1545
01:34:56,819 --> 01:34:57,779
[SPEAKER_00] kako je u Molenbiku,

1546
01:34:57,779 --> 01:34:59,979
[SPEAKER_00] kako je u Engleskoj

1547
01:34:59,979 --> 01:35:02,199
[SPEAKER_00] sa tim Pakistancima što smo govorili,

1548
01:35:02,199 --> 01:35:03,800
[SPEAKER_00] kako je u Švedskoj,

1549
01:35:03,800 --> 01:35:06,399
[SPEAKER_00] kako je u Francuskoj,

1550
01:35:06,399 --> 01:35:08,140
[SPEAKER_00] i nigdje nije dobro.

1551
01:35:08,140 --> 01:35:09,859
[SPEAKER_00] Nigdje to nije izašlo na dobro.

1552
01:35:12,180 --> 01:35:13,760
[SPEAKER_00] A opet, kažem, sa Srbima

1553
01:35:13,760 --> 01:35:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] smo stoljećima skupa.

1554
01:35:16,140 --> 01:35:18,319
[SPEAKER_00] i dio koji ne valja

1555
01:35:18,319 --> 01:35:20,720
[SPEAKER_00] je otkad,

1556
01:35:20,720 --> 01:35:22,659
[SPEAKER_00] reću vam kad je krenulo

1557
01:35:22,659 --> 01:35:23,239
[SPEAKER_00] na Izbrdu.

1558
01:35:23,239 --> 01:35:29,239
[SPEAKER_00] Kad smo išli

1559
01:35:29,239 --> 01:35:30,560
[SPEAKER_00] ka Prvom svjetskom ratu,

1560
01:35:30,560 --> 01:35:32,600
[SPEAKER_00] znači prije sto i toliko godina,

1561
01:35:32,600 --> 01:35:34,579
[SPEAKER_00] onda su, šta je zna,

1562
01:35:34,659 --> 01:35:36,680
[SPEAKER_00] Njemci su htjeli izgraditi

1563
01:35:36,680 --> 01:35:38,800
[SPEAKER_00] prugu Berlin-Bagdad.

1564
01:35:38,800 --> 01:35:41,840
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, htjeli su se povezati

1565
01:35:41,840 --> 01:35:44,239
[SPEAKER_00] sa Zapadnom Azijom,

1566
01:35:44,239 --> 01:35:45,319
[SPEAKER_00] s Bliskim Istokom,

1567
01:35:45,319 --> 01:35:46,739
[SPEAKER_00] radi trgovine,

1568
01:35:46,739 --> 01:35:47,560
[SPEAKER_00] radi razvoja,

1569
01:35:47,560 --> 01:35:50,560
[SPEAKER_00] radi nafte i tako dalje.

1570
01:35:50,560 --> 01:35:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] i onda su Britanci

1571
01:35:52,460 --> 01:35:54,220
[SPEAKER_00] odlučili da

1572
01:35:54,220 --> 01:35:56,020
[SPEAKER_00] Njemačku moraju

1573
01:35:56,020 --> 01:36:03,319
[SPEAKER_00] sabit u svoj prostor.

1574
01:36:03,319 --> 01:36:04,779
[SPEAKER_00] Malo srezat.

1575
01:36:04,779 --> 01:36:05,899
[SPEAKER_01] Staviti u...

1576
01:36:05,899 --> 01:36:06,939
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

1577
01:36:06,939 --> 01:36:08,939
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se zove ono...

1578
01:36:08,939 --> 01:36:11,939
[SPEAKER_00] Znači kad je stablo...

1579
01:36:11,939 --> 01:36:13,220
[SPEAKER_00] Obrezat, orezat.

1580
01:36:13,220 --> 01:36:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] Orezat, ne obrezat, orezat.

1581
01:36:15,039 --> 01:36:19,420
[SPEAKER_00] I uglavnom, onda su htjeli im

1582
01:36:19,420 --> 01:36:21,420
[SPEAKER_00] prekinuti tu prugu.

1583
01:36:21,420 --> 01:36:25,140
[SPEAKER_00] I onda su ustanovili da je u biti

1584
01:36:25,140 --> 01:36:28,140
[SPEAKER_00] ključni potez preko Srbije.

1585
01:36:28,140 --> 01:36:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] I onda su, šta,

1586
01:36:31,500 --> 01:36:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] odlučili su rušiti Njemačku

1587
01:36:33,000 --> 01:36:36,220
[SPEAKER_00] i odlučili su rušiti Tursko carstvo.

1588
01:36:36,220 --> 01:36:37,319
[SPEAKER_01] Otomansko.

1589
01:36:37,319 --> 01:36:38,060
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1590
01:36:38,060 --> 01:36:39,760
[SPEAKER_00] I oni su onda,

1591
01:36:39,760 --> 01:36:42,600
[SPEAKER_00] ušli su Britanci u Srbiju

1592
01:36:42,600 --> 01:36:43,939
[SPEAKER_00] i tako su pokrenuli

1593
01:36:43,939 --> 01:36:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Balkanske ratove

1594
01:36:45,000 --> 01:36:47,060
[SPEAKER_00] u kojima su Britanski časnici

1595
01:36:47,060 --> 01:36:48,800
[SPEAKER_00] zapovjedali tu

1596
01:36:48,800 --> 01:36:50,539
[SPEAKER_00] srpskim jedinicama.

1597
01:36:50,539 --> 01:36:53,279
[SPEAKER_00] Znači oni su aktivno sudjelovali

1598
01:36:53,279 --> 01:36:53,739
[SPEAKER_00] u tom,

1599
01:36:53,739 --> 01:36:55,880
[SPEAKER_00] u tim Balkanskim ratovima

1600
01:36:55,880 --> 01:36:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] da se,

1601
01:36:57,159 --> 01:36:59,600
[SPEAKER_00] da se istjera van

1602
01:36:59,600 --> 01:37:03,039
[SPEAKER_00] Osmanlijsko carstvo,

1603
01:37:03,039 --> 01:37:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] da se Tursko carstvo istjera iz Srbije

1604
01:37:05,000 --> 01:37:07,819
[SPEAKER_00] i da se prekine ta pruga,

1605
01:37:07,819 --> 01:37:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] da se,

1606
01:37:10,000 --> 01:37:12,260
[SPEAKER_00] da se Tursko carstvo i Njemačka povezu.

1607
01:37:12,640 --> 01:37:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] onako ekonomski

1608
01:37:13,880 --> 01:37:16,180
[SPEAKER_00] i znači da imaju tu neko

1609
01:37:16,180 --> 01:37:19,260
[SPEAKER_00] neko savezništvo i suradnju.

1610
01:37:19,260 --> 01:37:22,239
[SPEAKER_00] I oni su tu ušli u

1611
01:37:22,239 --> 01:37:25,100
[SPEAKER_00] vojne i obavještajne strukture

1612
01:37:25,100 --> 01:37:26,479
[SPEAKER_00] Srbije.

1613
01:37:27,760 --> 01:37:29,380
[SPEAKER_00] i mislim da do dana današnjeg

1614
01:37:29,380 --> 01:37:30,579
[SPEAKER_00] nisu izašli iz toga.

1615
01:37:30,579 --> 01:37:32,880
[SPEAKER_00] Da oni i do dana i današnjeg

1616
01:37:32,880 --> 01:37:34,739
[SPEAKER_00] kultiviraju te veze

1617
01:37:34,739 --> 01:37:36,159
[SPEAKER_00] i sad evo,

1618
01:37:36,159 --> 01:37:38,140
[SPEAKER_00] ovo što je Zadnje Milanović rekao,

1619
01:37:38,140 --> 01:37:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] bi bilo apsolutno sukladno tome,

1620
01:37:40,579 --> 01:37:41,220
[SPEAKER_00] zato što

1621
01:37:41,220 --> 01:37:43,300
[SPEAKER_00] ako je Izrael...

1622
01:37:43,939 --> 01:37:46,180
[SPEAKER_01] mislite, na ovu predsjednikovu izjavu...

1623
01:37:46,180 --> 01:37:47,479
[SPEAKER_00] Predsjednikovu izjavu da Izrael

1624
01:37:47,479 --> 01:37:51,359
[SPEAKER_00] naoružava Srbiju protiv Hrvatske.

1625
01:37:51,359 --> 01:37:53,680
[SPEAKER_00] To vam je opet ovo nastojanje

1626
01:37:53,680 --> 01:37:55,319
[SPEAKER_00] Britanskog carstva da pokrene

1627
01:37:55,319 --> 01:37:56,960
[SPEAKER_00] rat na Balkanu,

1628
01:37:56,960 --> 01:37:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] kao drugi front u sukobu

1629
01:37:59,619 --> 01:38:01,060
[SPEAKER_00] Zapada protiv Rusija

1630
01:38:01,060 --> 01:38:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] i da se treba nekako

1631
01:38:05,260 --> 01:38:06,760
[SPEAKER_00] nahuškat opet

1632
01:38:06,760 --> 01:38:08,020
[SPEAKER_00] Srbe protiv Hrvata,

1633
01:38:08,020 --> 01:38:09,539
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatsku protiv Srbije

1634
01:38:09,539 --> 01:38:10,479
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje.

1635
01:38:10,479 --> 01:38:12,460
[SPEAKER_00] I sad,

1636
01:38:12,460 --> 01:38:14,340
[SPEAKER_00] ako je Izrael

1637
01:38:14,340 --> 01:38:17,220
[SPEAKER_00] pod kontrolom

1638
01:38:17,220 --> 01:38:18,319
[SPEAKER_00] Britanskog carstva,

1639
01:38:18,319 --> 01:38:19,640
[SPEAKER_00] što smo spomenuli,

1640
01:38:19,640 --> 01:38:21,479
[SPEAKER_00] da je cijeli taj cionistički projekt,

1641
01:38:21,479 --> 01:38:23,840
[SPEAKER_00] proizvod

1642
01:38:23,840 --> 01:38:25,979
[SPEAKER_00] Britanskog imperija,

1643
01:38:25,979 --> 01:38:29,619
[SPEAKER_00] onda to opet ima smisla.

1644
01:38:29,619 --> 01:38:30,500
[SPEAKER_00] To je taj...

1645
01:38:30,500 --> 01:38:32,060
[SPEAKER_01] Onda vi opet nešto povezuje?

1646
01:38:32,060 --> 01:38:33,420
[SPEAKER_01] To je opet isti sukob.

1647
01:38:33,420 --> 01:38:35,680
[SPEAKER_00] To je opet isti sukob

1648
01:38:35,680 --> 01:38:37,619
[SPEAKER_00] koji se sada i nama nameče,

1649
01:38:37,619 --> 01:38:39,979
[SPEAKER_00] ne zato što smo mi njima

1650
01:38:39,979 --> 01:38:41,020
[SPEAKER_00] osobito važni,

1651
01:38:41,020 --> 01:38:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] niti im je Srbija osobito važna,

1652
01:38:43,460 --> 01:38:45,699
[SPEAKER_00] nego isto kako su upotrebili Srbiju

1653
01:38:45,699 --> 01:38:46,979
[SPEAKER_00] da se sukobe s Turcima

1654
01:38:46,979 --> 01:38:50,199
[SPEAKER_00] tokom Balkanskih ratova,

1655
01:38:50,199 --> 01:38:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] tako sada možda žele upotrebiti Srbiju

1656
01:38:52,880 --> 01:38:55,939
[SPEAKER_00] da se zarati protiv Hrvatske.

1657
01:38:55,939 --> 01:38:58,159
[SPEAKER_00] I nije im ni to toliko važno

1658
01:38:58,159 --> 01:38:59,020
[SPEAKER_00] koliko im je važno

1659
01:38:59,020 --> 01:38:59,939
[SPEAKER_00] da se onda uvuče

1660
01:38:59,939 --> 01:39:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] NATO u rat na Balkanu,

1661
01:39:01,960 --> 01:39:03,399
[SPEAKER_00] zato su nastavili

1662
01:39:03,399 --> 01:39:04,500
[SPEAKER_00] u savez s Albanijom,

1663
01:39:04,500 --> 01:39:05,079
[SPEAKER_00] s Bugarskom,

1664
01:39:05,079 --> 01:39:06,500
[SPEAKER_00] s kojima mi pak ništa nemamo,

1665
01:39:06,500 --> 01:39:08,279
[SPEAKER_00] ne vidi zašto bi mi imali

1666
01:39:08,279 --> 01:39:09,340
[SPEAKER_00] vojni savez s njima,

1667
01:39:09,340 --> 01:39:10,939
[SPEAKER_00] osim u ovom,

1668
01:39:10,939 --> 01:39:13,159
[SPEAKER_00] u okviru ovih planova

1669
01:39:13,159 --> 01:39:14,340
[SPEAKER_00] i da se onda,

1670
01:39:14,340 --> 01:39:15,300
[SPEAKER_00] kad je recimo

1671
01:39:15,300 --> 01:39:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] NATO uvučen

1672
01:39:17,199 --> 01:39:19,500
[SPEAKER_00] u rat protiv Srbije,

1673
01:39:19,500 --> 01:39:20,720
[SPEAKER_00] e onda ni Rusija

1674
01:39:20,720 --> 01:39:22,039
[SPEAKER_00] ne može ostati pasivno,

1675
01:39:22,039 --> 01:39:23,760
[SPEAKER_00] kao pasivni promatrač

1676
01:39:23,760 --> 01:39:27,020
[SPEAKER_00] i tako se onda opet Rusija nameće

1677
01:39:27,020 --> 01:39:29,220
[SPEAKER_00] drugi front.

1678
01:39:29,220 --> 01:39:34,220
[SPEAKER_00] A to je vrlo, vrlo slični scenarijo

1679
01:39:34,220 --> 01:39:37,479
[SPEAKER_00] kao 1914.

1680
01:39:38,220 --> 01:39:39,739
[SPEAKER_00] znači tu onda postoji rizik

1681
01:39:39,739 --> 01:39:42,520
[SPEAKER_00] da opet imamo generalni rat

1682
01:39:42,520 --> 01:39:45,500
[SPEAKER_00] na cijelom evropskom kontinentu,

1683
01:39:45,500 --> 01:39:47,020
[SPEAKER_00] koji je prije sto godina

1684
01:39:47,020 --> 01:39:49,939
[SPEAKER_00] završio sa 20 miliona mrtvih

1685
01:39:49,939 --> 01:39:51,680
[SPEAKER_00] i 40 miliona ukupno

1686
01:39:51,680 --> 01:39:53,779
[SPEAKER_00] ranjenih i nestalih,

1687
01:39:53,779 --> 01:39:56,039
[SPEAKER_00] a sad bi moglo biti puno gore.

1688
01:39:56,840 --> 01:39:57,859
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, njima je to ok,

1689
01:39:57,859 --> 01:39:58,399
[SPEAKER_00] jer oni

1690
01:39:58,399 --> 01:40:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] kroz rat ovi uvijek profitiraju.

1691
01:40:01,880 --> 01:40:02,460
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da,

1692
01:40:02,460 --> 01:40:04,180
[SPEAKER_01] više je profita kroz rat

1693
01:40:04,180 --> 01:40:04,880
[SPEAKER_01] nego kroz mir.

1694
01:40:04,880 --> 01:40:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da, apsolutno.

1695
01:40:05,960 --> 01:40:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] I sad, znate, bilo bi,

1696
01:40:07,500 --> 01:40:09,819
[SPEAKER_00] to je odgovor na pitanje

1697
01:40:09,819 --> 01:40:11,159
[SPEAKER_00] tko nam trese staklenku.

1698
01:40:11,159 --> 01:40:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] I onda umjesto da smo...

1699
01:40:13,119 --> 01:40:14,899
[SPEAKER_01] Već ova vaša antologijska izjava,

1700
01:40:14,899 --> 01:40:15,399
[SPEAKER_01] svi kažu

1701
01:40:15,399 --> 01:40:17,300
[SPEAKER_01] kako je Krajner objasnio

1702
01:40:17,300 --> 01:40:18,899
[SPEAKER_01] tko nam trese staklenku.

1703
01:40:18,899 --> 01:40:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1704
01:40:19,460 --> 01:40:21,640
[SPEAKER_01] Da, učit ćete u anale YouTube-a,

1705
01:40:21,640 --> 01:40:23,159
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno, odnosno podcasta.

1706
01:40:23,159 --> 01:40:24,779
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ali gledajte,

1707
01:40:24,779 --> 01:40:25,920
[SPEAKER_00] znate, to je važno

1708
01:40:25,920 --> 01:40:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] i to ne govori ja samo za Hrvate.

1709
01:40:27,880 --> 01:40:29,260
[SPEAKER_00] O tome trebaju razmišljati

1710
01:40:29,260 --> 01:40:31,260
[SPEAKER_00] i muslimani u Bosni,

1711
01:40:31,260 --> 01:40:32,659
[SPEAKER_00] i Srbi, i Crnogorci,

1712
01:40:32,659 --> 01:40:33,020
[SPEAKER_00] i svi,

1713
01:40:33,020 --> 01:40:33,899
[SPEAKER_00] jer smo,

1714
01:40:33,899 --> 01:40:35,600
[SPEAKER_00] svi smo mi u toj staklenci.

1715
01:40:35,600 --> 01:40:36,939
[SPEAKER_00] Svi mi tu živimo

1716
01:40:36,939 --> 01:40:37,640
[SPEAKER_00] gde smo,

1717
01:40:37,640 --> 01:40:39,060
[SPEAKER_00] na ovim prostorima

1718
01:40:39,060 --> 01:40:40,859
[SPEAKER_00] gde je neizbježno komunicirano,

1719
01:40:40,859 --> 01:40:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] komuniciramo,

1720
01:40:42,460 --> 01:40:43,560
[SPEAKER_00] premreženi smo

1721
01:40:43,560 --> 01:40:45,119
[SPEAKER_00] i moramo znat

1722
01:40:45,119 --> 01:40:49,399
[SPEAKER_00] da nas se u sukob gura.

1723
01:40:49,399 --> 01:40:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] Da nam je ta zamka

1724
01:40:53,119 --> 01:40:54,399
[SPEAKER_00] u biti stalno...

1725
01:40:54,920 --> 01:40:59,380
[SPEAKER_00] Samo je pitanje kad će neko uspjet fitilj pripalit

1726
01:40:59,380 --> 01:41:01,220
[SPEAKER_00] na dobar način.

1727
01:41:01,220 --> 01:41:02,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se nadam da baš i neće.

1728
01:41:02,720 --> 01:41:04,979
[SPEAKER_00] I znači, umjesto da budemo obsjednuti

1729
01:41:04,979 --> 01:41:07,140
[SPEAKER_00] šta se desilo prije 80 godina,

1730
01:41:07,140 --> 01:41:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] trebali bi biti obsjednuti s time

1731
01:41:09,079 --> 01:41:12,140
[SPEAKER_00] šta se može desiti u idućih 10 godina,

1732
01:41:12,140 --> 01:41:14,800
[SPEAKER_00] jer to onda definira budućnost

1733
01:41:14,800 --> 01:41:19,920
[SPEAKER_00] koju će na kraju krajeva proživljavati naša djeca.

1734
01:41:19,920 --> 01:41:23,659
[SPEAKER_00] Da li da završe kao žrtve rata

1735
01:41:23,659 --> 01:41:26,439
[SPEAKER_00] na nekom, u nekim blatnjavim rovovima

1736
01:41:26,439 --> 01:41:28,720
[SPEAKER_00] ili da živimo u miru, u blagostanju.

1737
01:41:28,720 --> 01:41:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da je to naš izbor

1738
01:41:31,699 --> 01:41:33,720
[SPEAKER_00] i zato moramo biti obsjednuti

1739
01:41:33,720 --> 01:41:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] s onima šta nam staklenku tresu,

1740
01:41:35,500 --> 01:41:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] a ne sa drugim mravima

1741
01:41:38,539 --> 01:41:39,880
[SPEAKER_00] koji su to isto staklenke.

1742
01:41:39,880 --> 01:41:41,739
[SPEAKER_00] U biti, sa tim drugim mravima

1743
01:41:41,739 --> 01:41:43,020
[SPEAKER_00] bi se trebali dogovoriti.

1744
01:41:43,020 --> 01:41:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad nam pro tresu staklenku pazi,

1745
01:41:47,000 --> 01:41:50,600
[SPEAKER_00] kontroliraj se, ne reagiraj odmah,

1746
01:41:50,600 --> 01:41:51,779
[SPEAKER_00] ne budi impulzivan,

1747
01:41:51,779 --> 01:41:55,420
[SPEAKER_00] stani na loptu i idemo malo razmisliti

1748
01:41:55,420 --> 01:41:57,020
[SPEAKER_00] o svemu prije nego što krenemo

1749
01:41:57,020 --> 01:41:59,100
[SPEAKER_00] u tučnjavu i pucnjavu.

1750
01:41:59,100 --> 01:42:01,140
[SPEAKER_01] Može još jedno pitanje?

1751
01:42:01,140 --> 01:42:02,220
[SPEAKER_00] Apsolutno.

1752
01:42:03,300 --> 01:42:04,340
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon ovog ćete,

1753
01:42:04,340 --> 01:42:06,760
[SPEAKER_01] nećete mi više htjeti doći.

1754
01:42:06,760 --> 01:42:10,960
[SPEAKER_01] Rekla sam da ste vani živjeli.

1755
01:42:10,960 --> 01:42:14,159
[SPEAKER_01] Nabrojali smo zemlje.

1756
01:42:14,159 --> 01:42:14,979
[SPEAKER_01] Imali zemlje,

1757
01:42:14,979 --> 01:42:16,880
[SPEAKER_01] sad ovo ne ispadne patetično.

1758
01:42:16,880 --> 01:42:18,279
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se, kad uspoređujete

1759
01:42:18,279 --> 01:42:19,300
[SPEAKER_01] taj život vani

1760
01:42:19,300 --> 01:42:20,199
[SPEAKER_01] i ovaj u Hrvatskoj

1761
01:42:20,199 --> 01:42:21,840
[SPEAKER_01] sad kad dođete doma,

1762
01:42:21,840 --> 01:42:24,119
[SPEAKER_01] gdje se bolje živi?

1763
01:42:24,119 --> 01:42:27,340
[SPEAKER_00] E, sad ću vam dat citat

1764
01:42:27,340 --> 01:42:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] mog sina.

1765
01:42:28,000 --> 01:42:28,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde.

1766
01:42:28,659 --> 01:42:30,760
[SPEAKER_00] Koji danas ima 15 godina.

1767
01:42:30,760 --> 01:42:32,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ima danas 15 godina,

1768
01:42:32,220 --> 01:42:32,880
[SPEAKER_00] ali je imao

1769
01:42:32,880 --> 01:42:33,939
[SPEAKER_00] ne danas,

1770
01:42:33,939 --> 01:42:35,100
[SPEAKER_00] ne da mu je danas rođena,

1771
01:42:35,100 --> 01:42:36,520
[SPEAKER_00] nego sad je imao 15 godina,

1772
01:42:36,520 --> 01:42:38,500
[SPEAKER_00] ali ova izjava

1773
01:42:38,500 --> 01:42:40,260
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi kad imao 8 godina.

1774
01:42:40,260 --> 01:42:40,600
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

1775
01:42:40,600 --> 01:42:41,140
[SPEAKER_00] mislim vam,

1776
01:42:41,140 --> 01:42:44,039
[SPEAKER_00] da vam dam ideju

1777
01:42:44,039 --> 01:42:45,680
[SPEAKER_00] od kuda je on došao

1778
01:42:45,680 --> 01:42:47,079
[SPEAKER_00] i gdje je on došao.

1779
01:42:47,840 --> 01:42:49,859
[SPEAKER_00] on se rodi u Monaku.

1780
01:42:49,859 --> 01:42:52,479
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo onda živjeli,

1781
01:42:52,479 --> 01:42:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] znači onda sam bio

1782
01:42:53,500 --> 01:42:55,659
[SPEAKER_00] u tim investicijskim krugovima,

1783
01:42:55,659 --> 01:42:57,100
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam relativno dobro živio,

1784
01:42:57,100 --> 01:42:58,319
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo živjeli u zgradi

1785
01:42:58,319 --> 01:43:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] u Marini,

1786
01:43:00,220 --> 01:43:01,739
[SPEAKER_00] u Monaku,

1787
01:43:01,739 --> 01:43:02,880
[SPEAKER_00] koja je ovako gledala

1788
01:43:02,880 --> 01:43:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] ravno na more.

1789
01:43:06,119 --> 01:43:07,800
[SPEAKER_00] meni je susjeda u zgradi

1790
01:43:07,800 --> 01:43:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] bila ova princeza Stefani.

1791
01:43:09,960 --> 01:43:13,439
[SPEAKER_00] Iz kuće smo imali

1792
01:43:13,439 --> 01:43:15,520
[SPEAKER_00] direktan izlaz u park,

1793
01:43:15,520 --> 01:43:18,520
[SPEAKER_00] zgrada imala svoj privatni bazen

1794
01:43:18,520 --> 01:43:20,619
[SPEAKER_00] na lukobranu.

1795
01:43:20,760 --> 01:43:21,560
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

1796
01:43:21,560 --> 01:43:25,460
[SPEAKER_00] nije da se u gazi rodio,

1797
01:43:25,460 --> 01:43:27,079
[SPEAKER_00] znači nije da se rodio

1798
01:43:27,079 --> 01:43:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] u nekom teškom,

1799
01:43:27,880 --> 01:43:32,520
[SPEAKER_00] znači to je njemu bila referenca,

1800
01:43:32,520 --> 01:43:33,319
[SPEAKER_00] to je bio svijet

1801
01:43:33,319 --> 01:43:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] koje on znao.

1802
01:43:34,960 --> 01:43:37,560
[SPEAKER_00] I onda jedan dan

1803
01:43:37,560 --> 01:43:39,239
[SPEAKER_00] smo tako došli u opatiju

1804
01:43:39,239 --> 01:43:41,319
[SPEAKER_00] i to je bio neko gluho vrijeme,

1805
01:43:41,319 --> 01:43:42,800
[SPEAKER_00] deseti mjesec.

1806
01:43:42,800 --> 01:43:45,520
[SPEAKER_00] Niš, niti plaža, niti sunce,

1807
01:43:45,520 --> 01:43:46,600
[SPEAKER_00] onako.

1808
01:43:46,600 --> 01:43:49,140
[SPEAKER_00] Došli smo posjetiti Nonića

1809
01:43:49,140 --> 01:43:51,079
[SPEAKER_00] i spustimo se ja

1810
01:43:51,079 --> 01:43:52,479
[SPEAKER_00] i on dolje do šetnice

1811
01:43:52,479 --> 01:43:53,319
[SPEAKER_00] na plažu

1812
01:43:53,319 --> 01:43:56,859
[SPEAKER_00] i on onako stoji na plaži

1813
01:43:56,859 --> 01:43:58,979
[SPEAKER_00] i gleda prema moru

1814
01:43:58,979 --> 01:43:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] zamišljeno

1815
01:43:59,619 --> 01:44:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže meni

1816
01:44:00,500 --> 01:44:02,260
[SPEAKER_00] tata, znaš,

1817
01:44:02,260 --> 01:44:05,260
[SPEAKER_00] baš je dobro da smo došli.

1818
01:44:05,260 --> 01:44:07,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem, zašto, Itan?

1819
01:44:07,539 --> 01:44:08,100
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže,

1820
01:44:08,100 --> 01:44:11,520
[SPEAKER_00] pa ništa podsjetilo mi je

1821
01:44:11,520 --> 01:44:12,460
[SPEAKER_00] da je ovdje bolje.

1822
01:44:12,460 --> 01:44:15,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo kažem, Itan,

1823
01:44:15,119 --> 01:44:16,220
[SPEAKER_00] šta je ovdje bolje?

1824
01:44:16,220 --> 01:44:18,899
[SPEAKER_00] On meni kaže, sve.

1825
01:44:19,140 --> 01:44:21,600
[SPEAKER_00] Razumijete?

1826
01:44:21,600 --> 01:44:22,100
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1827
01:44:22,100 --> 01:44:25,239
[SPEAKER_00] Sad, kako da vam ja interpretiraš

1828
01:44:25,239 --> 01:44:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] taj jedan osam godišnjak,

1829
01:44:27,000 --> 01:44:29,699
[SPEAKER_00] zašto on kaže da je ovdje sve bolje?

1830
01:44:29,699 --> 01:44:33,840
[SPEAKER_00] On ne mora brinuti ni o zdravstvenom osiguranju,

1831
01:44:33,840 --> 01:44:35,319
[SPEAKER_00] ni o plaćama, ni o penziji,

1832
01:44:35,319 --> 01:44:35,939
[SPEAKER_00] ni ti o ništa.

1833
01:44:35,939 --> 01:44:38,220
[SPEAKER_00] On naprosto vidi svijet kakav mu se,

1834
01:44:38,220 --> 01:44:39,859
[SPEAKER_00] kakav je pred njim.

1835
01:44:40,859 --> 01:44:41,260
[SPEAKER_00] i sad,

1836
01:44:41,260 --> 01:44:43,220
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje,

1837
01:44:43,220 --> 01:44:44,039
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam,

1838
01:44:44,039 --> 01:44:45,800
[SPEAKER_00] neko podneblje je,

1839
01:44:45,800 --> 01:44:47,260
[SPEAKER_00] pitom,

1840
01:44:47,260 --> 01:44:48,520
[SPEAKER_00] moja bivša supruga,

1841
01:44:48,520 --> 01:44:49,539
[SPEAKER_00] koja je amerikanka,

1842
01:44:49,539 --> 01:44:51,739
[SPEAKER_00] je bila zaljubljena u Hrvatsku.

1843
01:44:51,739 --> 01:44:52,319
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je,

1844
01:44:52,319 --> 01:44:54,680
[SPEAKER_00] ona je mene tjerala da se mi vratimo.

1845
01:44:54,680 --> 01:44:56,399
[SPEAKER_00] Ona kad je tu došla,

1846
01:44:56,399 --> 01:44:57,979
[SPEAKER_00] kad je upoznala ljude ovdje,

1847
01:44:57,979 --> 01:45:00,500
[SPEAKER_00] kad je upoznala malo Hrvatsku,

1848
01:45:00,500 --> 01:45:03,039
[SPEAKER_00] ona je mene preklijala da se mi vratimo.

1849
01:45:03,039 --> 01:45:04,079
[SPEAKER_00] što ja nisam mogo,

1850
01:45:04,079 --> 01:45:06,819
[SPEAKER_00] jer meni je posao bio tamo.

1851
01:45:06,819 --> 01:45:09,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se morao nacrtati u uredu svako jutro

1852
01:45:09,180 --> 01:45:11,159
[SPEAKER_00] i bilo je nerealno,

1853
01:45:11,159 --> 01:45:12,180
[SPEAKER_00] ali eto,

1854
01:45:12,180 --> 01:45:13,439
[SPEAKER_00] znači,

1855
01:45:13,439 --> 01:45:13,920
[SPEAKER_00] gledajte,

1856
01:45:13,920 --> 01:45:14,960
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam živio u Americi,

1857
01:45:14,960 --> 01:45:15,640
[SPEAKER_00] u Švicarskoj,

1858
01:45:15,640 --> 01:45:16,819
[SPEAKER_00] u Venecueli,

1859
01:45:16,819 --> 01:45:18,659
[SPEAKER_00] proput toga sam jako puno svijeta

1860
01:45:18,659 --> 01:45:21,479
[SPEAKER_00] i Tursku obalu,

1861
01:45:21,479 --> 01:45:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] i Grčku obalu,

1862
01:45:22,380 --> 01:45:23,579
[SPEAKER_00] i na Karibima,

1863
01:45:23,579 --> 01:45:25,020
[SPEAKER_00] nisam bio na svim otocima,

1864
01:45:25,020 --> 01:45:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu reći,

1865
01:45:25,699 --> 01:45:27,239
[SPEAKER_00] ali sam bio na puno njih.

1866
01:45:27,239 --> 01:45:30,619
[SPEAKER_00] I mene srce uvijek vuče nazad u Hrvatsku.

1867
01:45:30,619 --> 01:45:31,840
[SPEAKER_00] A ja nisam nostalgičar,

1868
01:45:31,880 --> 01:45:33,279
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne patim od nostalgije,

1869
01:45:33,279 --> 01:45:36,659
[SPEAKER_00] nego ja sam naprosto

1870
01:45:36,659 --> 01:45:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] dosta različitih kuhinja

1871
01:45:39,380 --> 01:45:40,720
[SPEAKER_00] probao da si kažem

1872
01:45:40,720 --> 01:45:42,619
[SPEAKER_00] naša mi je najbolja

1873
01:45:42,619 --> 01:45:43,739
[SPEAKER_00] i znam da nisam jedini.

1874
01:45:43,739 --> 01:45:45,760
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ima jako puno Hrvata

1875
01:45:45,760 --> 01:45:46,760
[SPEAKER_00] koji žive vani,

1876
01:45:46,760 --> 01:45:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] koji se žele vratiti.

1877
01:45:52,380 --> 01:45:54,560
[SPEAKER_00] A upoznao sam čak i Hrvata

1878
01:45:54,560 --> 01:45:56,579
[SPEAKER_00] koji su se rodili izvan Hrvatske,

1879
01:45:56,579 --> 01:45:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] kao moja djeca,

1880
01:45:57,840 --> 01:46:01,060
[SPEAKER_00] koji isto se žele vratiti.

1881
01:46:01,880 --> 01:46:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] Znači ja sam jednom

1882
01:46:03,119 --> 01:46:04,520
[SPEAKER_00] išao sam jedriti.

1883
01:46:04,520 --> 01:46:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] Bio mi je skiper,

1884
01:46:05,380 --> 01:46:06,199
[SPEAKER_00] nekakav tako,

1885
01:46:06,199 --> 01:46:07,220
[SPEAKER_00] taj dečko što je.

1886
01:46:07,220 --> 01:46:09,060
[SPEAKER_00] Jedva je Hrvatski govorio,

1887
01:46:09,060 --> 01:46:11,100
[SPEAKER_00] naučio je prvi moj jezik,

1888
01:46:11,100 --> 01:46:13,060
[SPEAKER_00] njemački u Švicarskoj.

1889
01:46:13,060 --> 01:46:17,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sve, sve, sve želi da se vrati.

1890
01:46:17,159 --> 01:46:18,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ne da se vrati,

1891
01:46:18,640 --> 01:46:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] tamo se rodio,

1892
01:46:19,699 --> 01:46:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] tamo je odraso,

1893
01:46:20,500 --> 01:46:22,180
[SPEAKER_00] ali došao u Hrvatsku,

1894
01:46:22,699 --> 01:46:24,380
[SPEAKER_00] osjetio da su mu tu korijeni

1895
01:46:24,380 --> 01:46:26,100
[SPEAKER_00] i rekao mi je,

1896
01:46:26,100 --> 01:46:26,420
[SPEAKER_00] čuj,

1897
01:46:26,420 --> 01:46:28,600
[SPEAKER_00] hoću ovdje živjeti,

1898
01:46:28,600 --> 01:46:29,800
[SPEAKER_00] hoću se ovdje vratiti.

1899
01:46:29,800 --> 01:46:31,159
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da,

1900
01:46:31,159 --> 01:46:33,720
[SPEAKER_00] sve ovo što,

1901
01:46:33,720 --> 01:46:35,659
[SPEAKER_00] kad živite ovdje,

1902
01:46:35,659 --> 01:46:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] uzimate zdravo za gotovo,

1903
01:46:37,380 --> 01:46:41,100
[SPEAKER_00] poslije shvatite da je,

1904
01:46:41,100 --> 01:46:42,079
[SPEAKER_00] da je u biti,

1905
01:46:42,079 --> 01:46:43,979
[SPEAKER_00] jedan čudesan,

1906
01:46:43,979 --> 01:46:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] čudesan dar,

1907
01:46:45,159 --> 01:46:46,779
[SPEAKER_00] da ovo imamo.

1908
01:46:46,779 --> 01:46:53,220
[SPEAKER_00] Trebali bi se malo bolje o tome brinuti

1909
01:46:53,220 --> 01:46:57,180
[SPEAKER_00] i malo to sa više srca i duša baštiniti,

1910
01:46:57,180 --> 01:47:01,319
[SPEAKER_00] rađe nego biti povodljivi za ovim,

1911
01:47:01,319 --> 01:47:01,979
[SPEAKER_00] znate,

1912
01:47:01,979 --> 01:47:09,199
[SPEAKER_00] Brisel i Strasburg i London i New York,

1913
01:47:09,199 --> 01:47:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] sve to o čemu ljudi sanjaju,

1914
01:47:10,960 --> 01:47:12,560
[SPEAKER_00] jer misle da je tamo bolje,

1915
01:47:12,560 --> 01:47:12,859
[SPEAKER_00] ali nije.

1916
01:47:12,859 --> 01:47:13,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ja tamo živim,

1917
01:47:13,619 --> 01:47:14,220
[SPEAKER_00] nije bolje.

1918
01:47:15,159 --> 01:47:16,239
[SPEAKER_01] Hoćete se vratiti?

1919
01:47:16,239 --> 01:47:18,479
[SPEAKER_00] Znate šta,

1920
01:47:18,479 --> 01:47:21,100
[SPEAKER_00] meni su djeca vani,

1921
01:47:21,100 --> 01:47:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] ja moram ostati u svojoj djeca,

1922
01:47:22,619 --> 01:47:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] jer su ja pre mali da ih prepustim,

1923
01:47:25,380 --> 01:47:28,279
[SPEAKER_00] sebe samima,

1924
01:47:28,279 --> 01:47:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali u dogledno vrijeme,

1925
01:47:29,460 --> 01:47:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] apsolutno da.

1926
01:47:30,199 --> 01:47:32,300
[SPEAKER_01] Čekamo vas onda,

1927
01:47:32,300 --> 01:47:33,899
[SPEAKER_00] razširenih rupu.

1928
01:47:33,899 --> 01:47:35,439
[SPEAKER_00] Jedva čekam da dođem.

1929
01:47:35,439 --> 01:47:36,960
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam.

1930
01:47:36,960 --> 01:47:38,939
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam na pozivu,

1931
01:47:38,939 --> 01:47:40,300
[SPEAKER_00] puno ste me tvari pitali,

1932
01:47:40,300 --> 01:47:41,819
[SPEAKER_00] tako da nisam Badava dolazio.

1933
01:47:41,819 --> 01:47:45,020
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad ne dođete Badava,

1934
01:47:45,159 --> 01:47:46,619
[SPEAKER_01] nadam da se...

1935
01:47:46,619 --> 01:47:48,979
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, uvijek mi je veselje

1936
01:47:48,979 --> 01:47:50,220
[SPEAKER_00] i drago mi je

1937
01:47:50,220 --> 01:47:53,119
[SPEAKER_00] i zahvalan sam na pozivu

1938
01:47:53,119 --> 01:47:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] i zahvalan sam na tome što

1939
01:47:55,619 --> 01:47:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi to i gledaju i slušaju,

1940
01:47:58,000 --> 01:48:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] znači da razmišljaju,

1941
01:48:00,199 --> 01:48:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] znači da smo

1942
01:48:00,960 --> 01:48:04,159
[SPEAKER_00] na dobrom putu,

1943
01:48:04,159 --> 01:48:05,479
[SPEAKER_00] jer toga nekad nije bilo.

1944
01:48:05,699 --> 01:48:07,159
[SPEAKER_00] nekad smo obisljeni o novinama

1945
01:48:07,159 --> 01:48:08,100
[SPEAKER_00] i o televiziji

1946
01:48:08,100 --> 01:48:10,720
[SPEAKER_00] i dalje od toga nismo vidjeli.

1947
01:48:10,720 --> 01:48:13,199
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je sjajno slušati danas

1948
01:48:13,199 --> 01:48:14,239
[SPEAKER_01] vaše razmišljanja,

1949
01:48:14,239 --> 01:48:15,220
[SPEAKER_01] a ova zahvala je

1950
01:48:15,220 --> 01:48:16,500
[SPEAKER_01] na najboljoj razini

1951
01:48:16,500 --> 01:48:17,640
[SPEAKER_01] Monegaškog dvora.

1952
01:48:17,640 --> 01:48:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala puno.

1953
01:48:20,619 --> 01:48:21,659
[SPEAKER_01] Alex Krajner,

1954
01:48:21,659 --> 01:48:22,819
[SPEAKER_01] bio je naš gost.

1955
01:48:22,819 --> 01:48:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam što nas gledate,

1956
01:48:24,000 --> 01:48:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] vidimo se vrlo brzo.

